a:5:{s:5:"title";s:72:"Vendasta Social Marketing now supports YouTube publishing and reporting";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:1238:"<p>Vendasta expanded Social Marketing with a YouTube API integration, adding YouTube as a managed channel alongside existing social destinations.</p>
<h3>What’s new</h3>
<p>Connect a YouTube channel to Social Marketing (Vendasta notes up to two channels per single location)</p>
<p>Draft, schedule, and publish videos directly from Social Marketing, including video metadata (title, description, etc.)</p>
<p>Manage YouTube posts through Post Composer and Campaign workflows</p>
<p>View basic performance metrics: Views, Likes, Comments, and overall Engagement</p>
<h3>Why it matters</h3>
<p>For teams managing multi-channel content calendars, the integration reduces context-switching by keeping YouTube publishing and light reporting inside the same workflow used for other social posts.</p>
<h3>Where to find it</h3>
<p>Connect: Social Marketing → Settings → Connect Accounts</p>
<p>Publish destinations: Post Composer, Post Campaign Composer</p>
<p>Learn more: <a href="https://roadmap.vendasta.com/changelog/available-now-publish-and-manage-youtube-videos-directly-in-social-marketing">https://roadmap.vendasta.com/changelog/available-now-publish-and-manage-youtube-videos-directly-in-social-marketing</a></p>
";s:9:"text-flow";a:12:{i:0;s:142:"Vendasta expanded Social Marketing with a YouTube API integration, adding YouTube as a managed channel alongside existing social destinations.";i:1;a:2:{i:0;s:2:"h2";i:1;s:12:"What’s new";}i:2;s:101:"Connect a YouTube channel to Social Marketing (Vendasta notes up to two channels per single location)";i:3;s:119:"Draft, schedule, and publish videos directly from Social Marketing, including video metadata (title, description, etc.)";i:4;s:65:"Manage YouTube posts through Post Composer and Campaign workflows";i:5;s:78:"View basic performance metrics: Views, Likes, Comments, and overall Engagement";i:6;a:2:{i:0;s:2:"h2";i:1;s:14:"Why it matters";}i:7;s:197:"For teams managing multi-channel content calendars, the integration reduces context-switching by keeping YouTube publishing and light reporting inside the same workflow used for other social posts.";i:8;a:2:{i:0;s:2:"h2";i:1;s:16:"Where to find it";}i:9;s:59:"Connect: Social Marketing → Settings → Connect Accounts";i:10;s:59:"Publish destinations: Post Composer, Post Campaign Composer";i:11;s:127:"Learn more: https://roadmap.vendasta.com/changelog/available-now-publish-and-manage-youtube-videos-directly-in-social-marketing";}s:4:"meta";a:2:{s:14:"links-required";a:0:{}s:18:"resources-detected";a:0:{}}}s:7:"summary";s:179:"Vendasta expanded Social Marketing with a YouTube API integration, adding YouTube as a managed channel alongside existing social destinations. | Read fresh CRM news at WeekCRM";s:14:"comments-count";i:0;s:9:"tags-data";a:2:{s:5:"ctree";a:3:{i:0;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:3:"CRM";s:4:"href";s:34:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/crm/";}i:1;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:15:"product updates";s:4:"href";s:46:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/product-updates/";}i:2;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:8:"vendasta";s:4:"href";s:39:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/vendasta/";}}s:20:"all-resnames-uploads";a:0:{}}}